@startuml SignalReport - Sequenz PDF-Export
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceFontSize 13
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1
skinparam roundcorner 10

actor Benutzer
participant Browser
participant WebServer
participant PdfReportGenerator
participant H2MeasurementRepository
database H2_Database as DB
participant JFreeChart
participant OpenPDF

Benutzer -> Browser : Klicke "PDF-Bericht (24h)"
Browser -> WebServer : GET /api/report?hours=24

WebServer -> PdfReportGenerator : new PdfReportGenerator(repo)
WebServer -> PdfReportGenerator : generateReport(24)

PdfReportGenerator -> H2MeasurementRepository : calculateStatistics("PING", 24)
H2MeasurementRepository -> DB : SELECT latency_ms, success FROM measurements WHERE timestamp >= ...
DB --> H2MeasurementRepository : Ergebnisse
H2MeasurementRepository --> PdfReportGenerator : Statistics (avg, p95, max, loss, jitter)

PdfReportGenerator -> H2MeasurementRepository : findLastN(144)
H2MeasurementRepository -> DB : SELECT ... ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 144
DB --> H2MeasurementRepository : 144 Messungen
H2MeasurementRepository --> PdfReportGenerator : List<Measurement>

PdfReportGenerator -> JFreeChart : createXYLineChart()
JFreeChart --> PdfReportGenerator : JFreeChart-Objekt
PdfReportGenerator -> JFreeChart : render als BufferedImage

PdfReportGenerator -> OpenPDF : new Document()
PdfReportGenerator -> OpenPDF : add(Paragraph "SignalReport – Bericht")
PdfReportGenerator -> OpenPDF : add(Paragraph "Statistiken")
PdfReportGenerator -> OpenPDF : add(Image chartImage)
OpenPDF --> PdfReportGenerator : PDF-Bytes

PdfReportGenerator --> WebServer : byte[] pdfBytes
WebServer -> Browser : HTTP 200 + Content-Disposition: attachment
Browser -> Benutzer : Speichere PDF-Datei

note over PdfReportGenerator, OpenPDF
  PDF enthält:
  • Titel + Zeitraum
  • 5 Statistiken (avg, p95, max, loss, jitter)
  • Latenz-Chart als Bild
end note
@enduml